review.reviewBody: Was tasty, quite rich - could have used a bit more sauce otherwise good
This is defintely not a New York Steak 10oz, its tiny  Also, I was supposed to receive mashed potatoes and seasonal veggies, not fries and the world's smallest salad.
There was less sauce and chicken than usual. Not enough to cover the pasta
